 However, the standard archive files are produced at a rate of 1 Hz, and
 each sample is the average of 50 samples.
 Therefore, the time associated with measurements reported at 1
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

Hz is actually an average over the specified second, so the reference time
 for the averaged measurement is actually 0.5
